      "method": "PATCH",
      "path": "/api/v1/admin/integration-settings/payment-settings",
      "body_note": "Flat object OR { \"settings\": { ... } }. Values are usually strings \"0\"/\"1\" and env \"test\"/\"live\"/\"sandbox\". Only sent keys are upserted (ThirdPartySetting module payment).",
